  "title": "SUPERVISOR",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><p>* Oversee efficiency of operational processes</p><p>* Participate in strategic planning and goal-setting for various business functions</p><p>* Analyze business requirements and customer needs</p><p>* Research methods to improve operations and reduce costs</p><p>* Monitor and report on department performance</p><p>* Supervise and train employees</p><p>* Provide administrative support (e.g. updating inventory)</p><p>* Ensure compliance with company policies and regulation</p><p>* Able to work on weekend and public holiday</p><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><p>* Previous experience as an operations supervisor or similar role</p><p>* Hands-on experience implementing operational processes</p><p>* Excellent project management skills</p><p>* Knowledge of operational principles and policies</p><p>* Organisational skills and attention to detail</p><p>* Team leadership</p>",
